"GRADUAL": "Proceeding by steps or degrees; advancing, step by step, as inascent or descent or from one state to another; regularlyprogressive; slow; as, a gradual increase of knowledge; a gradualdecline.Creatures animate with gradual life Of growth, sense, reason, allsummed up in man. Milton.",
